cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestDeployAgent -v`\n63: \n64: - [x] **T1.10**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status` method\n65:   - Purpose: Get Deployment and Service status from Kubernetes\n66:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:260-292`\n67:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestGetAgentStatus -v`\n68: \n69: - [x] **T1.11**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.delete_agent` method\n70:   - Purpose: Delete Deployment and Service, ignore 404 errors\n71:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:294-319`\n72:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestDeleteAgent -v`\n73: \n74: ### Phase 2: AgentCubeProvider Implementation (ST-2)\n75: \n76: - [x] **T2.1**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider.__init__` with namespace, verbose, kubeconfig params\n77:   - Purpose: Initialize provider with CustomObjectsApi for CR management\n78:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:18-37`\n79:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestAgentCubeProviderInit -v`\n80: \n81: - [x] **T2.2**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider` constants (CR_GROUP, CR_VERSION, CR_PLURAL, timeouts)\n82:   - Purpose: Define AgentRuntime CRD constants and default timeouts\n83:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:11-16`\n84:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestConstants -v`\n85: \n86: - [x] **T2.3**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider._sanitize_name` helper\n87:   - Purpose: Sanitize agent names for AgentRuntime CR naming (same logic as K8sProvider)\n88:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:185-190`\n89:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestSanitizeName -v`\n90: \n91: - [x] **T2.4**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider._ensure_namespace` helper\n92:   - Purpose: Ensure target namespace exists for CR deployment\n93:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:169-183`\n