{"type":"text","timestamp":1775878934331,"sessionID":"ses_2855e993bffex8QV8kEBx24qSH","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa1e914001LR7JCVeM6QJc4h","messageID":"msg_d7aa1cde5001Fnd714wyoUcyE8","sessionID":"ses_2855e993bffex8QV8kEBx24qSH","type":"text","text":"Based on the tasks.md and design.md files:\n\n## Summary for AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider\n\n### Completed (100% - 73/73 tasks)\n\n**Phase 1-2: Provider Implementations**\n- `KubernetesProvider` (11 tasks): Deployment + NodePort Service management, name sanitization, namespace handling, readiness polling\n- `AgentCubeProvider` (7 tasks): AgentRuntime CR management with CustomObjectsApi, CRD constants, readiness probes, imagePullSecrets\n\n**Phase 3-4: Unit Tests** (43 tests)\n- KubernetesProvider: 23 tests covering init, sanitize_name, ensure_namespace, create_deployment, create_service, wait_for_ready, deploy_agent, get_status, delete_agent\n- AgentCubeProvider: 20 tests covering init, constants, sanitize_name, ensure_namespace, deploy_agent_runtime, get_agent_runtime, delete_agent_runtime, readiness_probe, imagePullSecrets\n\n**Phase 5-6: Runtime Integration** (29 tasks)\n- `PublishRuntime`, `InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime` with provider selection, endpoint rewriting for AgentRuntime CR, session ID management\n\n**Phase 7: Package Export**\n- Both providers exported from `agentcube.services` package\n\n### Deferred\n\n**None explicitly deferred** - all acceptance criteria met. \n\n**Out of scope per design.md (integration testing)**:\n- Integration tests requiring running Kubernetes cluster\n- Volcano AgentCube CRDs installation for real AgentCubeProvider validation\n- End-to-end CLI command testing","time":{"start":1775878934329,"end":1775878934329}}}
